  "detailed_description": "<h1>EARLY ACCESS ROADMAP</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/4a144f40634cb0a40498800e7a1568fd.avif?t=1667408432\" width=600 height=793 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Your life as a captain is over! Or is it?..  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/61d49f9b66ae16176945b7a9ae7dd8ee.poster.avif?t=1667408432\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/61d49f9b66ae16176945b7a9ae7dd8ee.webm?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/61d49f9b66ae16176945b7a9ae7dd8ee.mp4?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Soul fragments scattered, they've got their own plans for your essence! Make peace with your past, or blow it up!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/8671995d0097d290b83df317ad62a429.poster.avif?t=1667408432\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/8671995d0097d290b83df317ad62a429.webm?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/8671995d0097d290b83df317ad62a429.mp4?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Build, bargain and battle your way back to the land of the living in this top-down strategy shooter! </strong>Do you have what it takes to be a Solar Scion?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build space stations & AI ships<br></li><li>Make & sell power-ups<br></li><li>Upgrade planets & ships<br></li><li>Capture control points<br></li><li>Harvest & trade resources<br></li><li>Beware dangerous nebulas<br></li><li>..On a quest to return to life!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Your life as a captain is over! Or is it?..  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/61d49f9b66ae16176945b7a9ae7dd8ee.poster.avif?t=1667408432\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/61d49f9b66ae16176945b7a9ae7dd8ee.webm?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/61d49f9b66ae16176945b7a9ae7dd8ee.mp4?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Soul fragments scattered, they've got their own plans for your essence! Make peace with your past, or blow it up!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/8671995d0097d290b83df317ad62a429.poster.avif?t=1667408432\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/8671995d0097d290b83df317ad62a429.webm?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1395510/extras/8671995d0097d290b83df317ad62a429.mp4?t=1667408432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Build, bargain and battle your way back to the land of the living in this top-down strategy shooter! </strong>Do you have what it takes to be a Solar Scion?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build space stations & AI ships<br></li><li>Make & sell power-ups<br></li><li>Upgrade planets & ships<br></li><li>Capture control points<br></li><li>Harvest & trade resources<br></li><li>Beware dangerous nebulas<br></li><li>..On a quest to return to life!</li></ul>",
